Update the MkDocs Configuration

Update the MkDocs Configuration

This new structure for MkDocs pages configuration was released with MkDocs
version 0.13 (release 2015-05-27). It is a much cleaner and clearer way to
represent your page tree (and allows further nesting beyond a top level and
second level).
Encouraging devs to run tests before PRs.

Upgraded Django installed in projects to 1.3

Due to the slower path 0.9 has taken the Pinax team we've decided we need to
ship with the newest version of Django (we really do plan on have 0.9 done
before 1.4). Pinax itself needs to continue running on 1.2 (this may be a bit
selfish, but there's a ton out there still using 1.2). All new projects can
take advantage of the new features 1.3 has to offer.
Cleaned up MANIFEST.in and used more splats because there is no reason we wouldn't want everything in these paths (also cuts down on the number of warnings given by setuptools)
